  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13088735/equipment.jpg" alt="Insider Guides: Snow + Rock Top Picks – Equipment" data-udi="umb://media/38be1932d2aa49ea9467a2e57ea2b299" /></p>
<p>We’ve teamed up with the experts from Snow+Rock, to discover their top picks of the latest ski and snowboard gear to hit the slopes in this winter. All Inghams guests will receive a <strong>12.5% discount code</strong> with <a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/"><strong>Snow+Rock</strong></a>. Seen something you like below? Check out our ski offers here to find the best resort to show off your new ski style.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" class="c-btn">View ski resorts</a></p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="color: #003155;">Men's Piste Gear</h3>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/j-lindeberg-mens-base-camp-ski-jacket-H1114567.html?colour=98" data-anchor="?colour=98"><img style="width: 51px; height: 77px; float: right;" src="/media/13088906/jlindeburg-basecamp-jacket-3.jpg" alt="J. Lindeberg Basecamp Jacket" data-udi="umb://media/84be061c8d8244c381de0088b025c020" /></a></p>
<p><strong>J. Lindeberg Basecamp Jacket</strong> <br />Designed for those who want to make an impact. With advanced fabric technology, it not only looks great but is built for life on the mountains. Mechanical stretch fabric heightens your freedom while the waterproof, windproof and breathable TX SHELL 2L protects you from the elements.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/salomon-mens-s-max-120-gw-ski-boot-J1114175.html?colour=3624" data-anchor="?colour=3624"><img style="width: 75px; height: 75px; float: right;" src="/media/13088905/salomon-s-max-120-gw-1.jpg" alt="Salomon S/MAX 120 GW Boots" data-udi="umb://media/4a75c11d57174a389e9410b5fc45d428" /></a><strong>Salomon S/MAX 120 GW Boots</strong><br />A revolutionary boot, the Salomon S/MAX 120 GW has a Coreframe construction with a thinner shell to make them lighter, more agile and more sensitive for improved power transmission. The Custom Shell HD makes the pre-shaped seamless liner customisable in just 10 minutes for ultimate comfort on piste.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/bolle-men-s-v-line-visor-snow-helmet-I2114575.html?colour=124" data-anchor="?colour=124"><img style="width: 75px; height: 75px; float: right;" src="/media/13088912/bolle-v-line-photochromatic-visor-helmet-1.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/fc15aef1b43c45fcb83dd99e1eb95350" /></a><strong>Bolle V-Line Photochromic Visor Helmet</strong><br />Injected with high-quality ABS for solid resistance and high-capacity shock absorption, this is one of Bolle's most advanced helmets. The built-in visor features Phantom’s highest quality photochromic flash mirror lens for exceptional protection against the rays.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="color: #003155;">Women's Piste Gear</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/toni-sailer-sports-womens-sestriere-new-pant-H3214742.html?colour=124" data-anchor="?colour=124"><img style="width: 75px; height: 100px; float: right;" src="/media/13088904/toni-sailor-sestriere-pant.jpg" alt="Toni Sailer Sestriere Pant" data-udi="umb://media/b05596b6636345f3bd02d667652023f4" /></a><strong>Toni Sailer Sestriere Pant</strong> <br />This longstanding bestseller is a staple in many skiers wardrobes! As well as a flattering tailored fit, this Pant has the technology to keep up with the most active skiers, including pre-shaped knees, a high waistband and elasticated snow gaiters.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/salomon-mens-s-max-10-skis-m11-gw-l80-binding-J1314385.html?colour=3651" data-anchor="?colour=3651"><img style="width: 75px; height: 150px; float: right;" src="/media/13088902/salomon-s-max-w-10.jpg" alt="Salomon S/MAX W 10 Skis" data-udi="umb://media/0c99feb870ea481f929b3dd44fe44bb6" /></a><strong>Salomon S/MAX W 10 Ski &amp; Bindings</strong><br />If pushing your limits at every turn is your goal, you need the Salomon S/MAX W 10. This modern high-performance ski has a unique shape that helps you feel in control, giving you the confidence to carve perfect turns and push the boundaries of what’s possible.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/smith-men-s-4d-mag-goggle-I1114214.html?colour=2921" data-anchor="?colour=2921"><img style="width: 75px; height: 75px; float: right;" src="/media/13088900/smith-4d-mag.jpg" alt="Smith 4D MAG Goggles" data-udi="umb://media/fd6e7f6b3af5426aae2e5a83e08aeec6" /></a></p>
<p><strong>Smith 4D MAG Goggles</strong><br />The only goggle you need for all-condition riding, it combines ChromaPop™ technology with quick and easy lens-change tech, while a wide field of vision gives you a better view.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="color: #003155;">All Mountain Men's Gear</h3>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/patagonia-mens-powder-bowl-jacket-H1114500.html?colour=133" data-anchor="?colour=133"><img style="width: 51px; height: 77px; float: right;" src="/media/13088919/patagonia-powder-bowl-jacket.jpg" alt="Patagonia Powder Bowl Jacket" data-udi="umb://media/1ac4513edf464522a3e85431d6a499a1" /></a><strong>Patagonia Powder Bowl Jacket</strong><br />Impervious to all conditions, this jacket will become your new best friend on the slopes. Built with 100% recycled GORE-TEX face fabric, it protects against the elements, while a refined fit ensures this jacket not only delivers, but looks the part while doing so.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/patagonia-mens-powder-bowl-pants-H1214297.html?colour=157" data-anchor="?colour=157"><img style="width: 51px; height: 82px; float: right;" src="/media/13088918/patagonia-powder-bowl-pant.jpg" alt="Patagonia Powder Bowl Pant" data-udi="umb://media/f668c28d987948389f27f01231f24639" /></a><strong>Patagonia Powder Bowl Pant</strong><br />Perfect for those who love to stay on the slopes when the crowds call it a day, these pants deliver maximum protection with minimal impact. Recycled polyester fabric provides breathable insulation, whilst a two-layer GORE-TEX and durable water repellent finish offers unrivalled protection and the articulated knees give you the freedom for spontaneous aerials.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/volkl-men-s-deacon-80-skis-with-lowride-xl-13-fr-gw-binding-J1324230.html?colour=180" data-anchor="?colour=180"><img style="width: 95px; height: 61px; float: right;" src="/media/13088920/volkl-deacon-80.jpg" alt="Volkl Deacon 80 Skis" data-udi="umb://media/88288b7b2b3448a4a1dba8bfc4abf8ad" /></a><strong>Völkl Deacon 80 Ski &amp; Bindings</strong><br />For those who don’t want to compromise, this ski is constructed using 3D. Ridge and 3D.Glass and features Vokl’s 3D radius sidecut technology, which is sure to make you feel at home wherever you ski.<br />Its built-in LowRide XL binding, with GripWalk compatibility, offers a low stand height for more direct feel and better power transfer.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="color: #003155;">All Mountain Women's Gear</h3>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/picture-womens-seen-jacket-H3115448.html?colour=98" data-anchor="?colour=98"><img style="width: 66px; height: 88px; float: right;" src="/media/13088903/picture-seen-jacket.jpg" alt="Picture Seen Jacket" data-udi="umb://media/1f43cbc7b9044c8d917fc4bcbe6cedf7" /></a><strong>Picture Seen Jacket</strong> <br />Made sustainably, with the Picture Seen Jacket you can look good and feel good. Their innovative approach uses bio-sourced fabrics and PFC-free membranes for ethical yet long-lasting waterproof breathability. While keeping you warm is a Coremax lining which eliminates cold spots, and a Thermal Dry System, which wicks away moisture.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/picture-womens-haakon-bib-H3214900.html?colour=124" data-anchor="?colour=124"><img style="width: 91px; height: 121px; float: right;" src="/media/13088917/picture-haakon-bib.jpg" alt="Picture Haakon Bib Pant" data-udi="umb://media/2b8746849de4453c95ff44c8463ca7ce" /></a><strong>Picture Haakon Bib Pant</strong><br />The ultimate freeride bib, the Haakon Bib is a two-layer, lightweight and functional pant providing complete protection. The removable bib and adjustable suspenders make it versatile, whatever the terrain and however hard you choose to play. Redefining what is possible, Picture utilises sustainable materials to provide exceptional protection with minimum impact.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"> </p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/atomic-womens-hawx-ultra-95-s-gw-ski-boot-J1214275.html?colour=117" data-anchor="?colour=117"><img style="width: 83px; height: 83px; float: right;" src="/media/13088916/atomic-hawx-ultra-95-s-w-gw-1.jpg" alt="Atomic HAWX ULTRA 95 S W GW" data-udi="umb://media/20412030678c4260975ef0191d97aab2" /></a><strong>Atomic HAWX ULTRA 95 S W GW Boots</strong><br />Perfect for all-mountain skiers, the Atomic Hawx Ultra 95 S W GW delivers the legendary Hawk feel and performance. The slimmer profile creates a lightweight shell that is 25% more stable than its predecessor. A heat-moldable liner enables you to get a fully tailored fit, while the Adaptive Fit System Cuff features a removable spoiler for adjustable volume.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="color: #003155;">Snowboarding Men's Gear</h3>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/burton-mens-ak-2l-swash-gtx-jacket-H1112640.html?colour=893" data-anchor="?colour=893"><img style="width: 66px; height: 88px; float: right;" src="/media/13088907/burton-swash-jacket.jpg?width=300&amp;height=400" alt="Burton [ak] GORE-TEX Swash Jacket" data-udi="umb://media/31baf0b6f73b43e6ab21d00cf1e9af58" /></a><strong>Burton Men's [ak] GORE-TEX Swash Jacket</strong><br />One of the smartest jackets in snowboarding! The PrimaLoft insulation focuses warmth around your core for enhanced manoeuvrability, while the GORE-SEAM tape seals against wind and water, and the lightweight, down-proof lining provides fast wicking and breathability. Add to this Powder Gasket Cuffs, a water-repellent waist gaiter and water-resistant zippers, and you’ll be on the slopes all day.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/burton-mens-family-tree-3d-daily-driver-snowboard-J2324563.html?colour=117" data-anchor="?colour=117"><img style="width: 72px; height: 91px; float: right;" src="/media/13088908/burton-family-tree-3d-snowboard.jpg" alt="Burton Family Tree 3D Daily Driver" data-udi="umb://media/882508bdfffb42b2bf6da90b74894d85" /></a><strong>Burton Family Tree 3D Daily Driver Snowboard</strong><br />Built for riders by riders, this is the go-to board for versatility. Combining surfboard-inspired convex shaping in the tip and tail with a traditional base contour through the middle gives impressive edge control and a fluid feel in all snow conditions.<br />The Burton Cartel X Re:Flex bindings are lightweight and durable, with the latest technology to keep you safe and advanced AutoCANT cushioning, which automatically tilts to put you in the most comfortable position.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/salomon-mens-dialogue-lace-str8jkt-boa-snowboard-boot-J2124232.html?colour=2024" data-anchor="?colour=2024"><img style="width: 75px; height: 95px; float: right;" src="/media/13088922/salomon-dialogue-lace-boot.jpg" alt="&lt;strong&gt;Salomon Dialogue Lace STR8JKT BOA" data-udi="umb://media/dc3e1b88c1814e31ae84eed603a24b6a" /></a><strong>Salomon Dialogue Lace STR8JKT BOA Boot</strong><br />Salomon’s latest boot, the Dialogue Lace STR8JKT BOA, marks the return of a stiffer, all-mountain boot. Featuring fit to ride technology developed with athletes, they combine durability and lightweight feel to deliver comfort and performance from the moment you pull them on, right through to your last run.</p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="color: #003155;">Snowboarding Women's Gear</h3>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/burton-womens-amora-pants-H3214891.html?colour=157" data-anchor="?colour=157"><img style="width: 91px; height: 105px; float: right;" src="/media/13088909/burton-amora-pant.jpg" alt="Burton Amora Anorak Pants" data-udi="umb://media/fcae555c68e54dc98ab2664c6b60eb0b" /></a><strong>Burton Women's Amora Anorak Pants</strong><br />This wearable mid-rise pant is ideal for whole days on the mountains. With Burton’s Living Lining, you get the benefit of automatic climate control without added bulk or weight, so you can count on consistent comfort, while advanced waterproofing keeps you dry when the conditions get tough.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/burton-womens-felix-step-on-snowboard-boot-J2230018.html?colour=124" data-anchor="?colour=124"><img style="width: 91px; height: 105px; float: right;" src="/media/13088914/burton-felix-step-on.jpg" alt="Burton Felix Step On Boots" data-udi="umb://media/a997a21014ae49fa8c41a33c3771c8ee" /></a><strong>Burton Women's Felix Step On Boots</strong><br />The boot to choose for the highest level of performance and greatest comfort. Featuring effortless adjustment and precision fit Dual Zone BOA® Coiler Closure System, you’ll spend less time getting your kit sorted and more time on the slopes.</p>
<p style="float-right: 40px;"><a href="https://www.snowandrock.com/p/oakley-flight-deck-goggles-I1112697.html?colour=3657" data-anchor="?colour=3657"><img style="width: 105px; height: 75px; float: right;" src="/media/13088913/oakley-flight-deck-goggles.jpg" alt="Oakley Flight Deck L Goggles" data-udi="umb://media/f62f919df732475a9d99e3ef21f9b6a7" /></a><strong>Oakley Flight Deck L Goggles</strong><br />Taking inspiration from the helmet visor of fighter pilots, the Oakley Flight Deck maximises your field of view, while Ridgelock Technology allows for quick and easy lens changes without compromising lens seal.</p>
